# Project Context: Akrab Pharma
- Architecture: Clean Architecture.
- State Management: Provider.
- Database: Supabase.
- Project Location: Algeria (El Taref).

# Structure Rules:
- DO NOT rename existing files or classes.
- Models: lib/models/ (e.g., duty_pharmacy.dart).
- Services: lib/services/ (e.g., pharmacy_fetcher.dart, gps_service.dart).
- Views: lib/views/ (e.g., home_screen.dart).
- Widgets: lib/widgets/ (e.g., shimmer_loading.dart).

# Coding Standards:
- Always use null-safety.
- Keep UI logic separated from data logic.
- When implementing new features, reference the existing services (pharmacy_fetcher, gps_service).
- Always use the existing '_PharmacyCard' widget inside home_screen.dart when displaying list items.
